Iiran knights provide such big
help to everyone in shopping ward.
We owe huge debt of gratitude!

rows.label: tlk70000038_03_msg0002
rows.name:
That why we thinking about how
we can celebrate together.

rows.label: tlk70000038_03_msg0003
rows.name: But Boss got angry at plans we made...

rows.label: tlk70000038_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Said that we have to be more careful
to plan this kind of thing, otherwise
might be accused of corrupty-cahoots.

rows.label: tlk70000038_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Boss really thinking lots about you,
even if in own particular way...

rows.label: tlk70000038_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Wish I got half the concern...
He never ever notice Popolo's
increasing overtime...
